'''Circus''' ndi msewu mbiri lalikulu [[Townhouse|townhouses]] mu mzinda wa [[Bath, Somerset]] , [[England]] , kupanga bwalo ndi zipata zitatu.  Chinapangidwa ndi otchuka [[Architect|wamanga]] [[John Wood, the Elder|John Wood, Wamkulu]] , izo inayambika mu 1754, anamaliza mu 1768, ndipo ankamuona ngati chitsanzo chachikulu koposa a [[Georgian architecture|zomangamanga Chijojiya]] .  Dzina limachokera ku [[Chilatini|Latin]] 'circus', kutanthauza mphete, oval kapena bwalo.  Yakhala yosankhidwa ngati nyumba [[Listed building|yowonjezeredwa]]. 

Circus imagawidwa m'magulu atatu a kutalika kwake, ndi udzu pakati.  Gawo lirilonse likuyang'ana limodzi la masitepe atatu, kutsimikizira kuti nkhope yapamwamba nthawizonse imayikidwa molunjika kutsogolo. 

== Mbiri ==
[[File:The_Circus_Bath_20040731.jpg|thumb| Circus]]
Circus, yomwe poyamba inatchedwa '''King's Circus''' , inapangidwa ndi [[Architect|wokonza mapulani]] [[John Wood, the Elder|John Wood, Mkulu]] .  Anatsimikiza kuti Bath anali malo oyambirira a ntchito ya [[Druid]] ku Britain, Wood omwe anagwidwa ndi [[Stonehenge]] , omwe ali ndi {{Convert|325|ft}}   ku outer bank bank, ndipo adapanga Circus ndi {{Convert|318|ft}}   kuti azitsanzira izi.  

Wood anafa pasanathe miyezi itatu kuchokera pamene mwala woyamba unayikidwa; mwana wake, [[John Wood, the Younger|John Wood, Wamng'ono]] , adamaliza ntchitoyi popanga mapangidwe a abambo ake.  Ndalama zoyamba za kumwera kwakumadzulo zinaperekedwa mu 1755-1767, gawo lakumwera chakummawa mu 1762-1766, ndi gawo la kumpoto mu 1764-1766. 

== Kupanga ==
Malamulo atatu a [[Classical order|m'Chikatolika]] (Greek [[Doric order|Doric]] , [[Roman/Composite order|Roman / Composite]] ndi [[Corinthian order|Korinto]] ) amagwiritsidwa ntchito, pamwamba pa zina, muzithunzi zam'mbali zokongola.  The [[frieze]] wa [[Doric order|Doric]] [[entablature]] ali chokongoletsedwa ndi alternating [[Triglyph|triglyphs]] ndi 525 zithunzi zizindikiro, kuphatikizapo njoka, zizindikiro kuyendetsa sitima zapamadzi, zipangizo woimira zaluso ndi masayansi, ndi [[Freemasonry#Ritual, symbolism, and morality|zizindikiro masonic]] .  The [[Parapet|kampanda]] ili ndi mwala Kanthanga [[Finial|finials]] . 

Poyang'ana kuchokera mlengalenga, Circus, pamodzi ndi Queens Square ndi [[Gay Street, Bath|Gay Street yomwe]] ikugwirizana nawo, amapanga mawonekedwe ofunikira, omwe ndi chizindikiro cha masonic chofanana ndi chokongoletsera nyumba zambiri za Wood.  

Chigawo chapakati chinali ndi miyala yokhala ndi miyala, yomwe inali pakhomo lomwe linapereka madzi ku nyumba.  Mu 1800 anthu ozungulira Circus adalumikiza mbali yapakatikati ya malo osatsegula ngati munda.  Tsopano, dera lapakatili liri udzu pamwamba ndipo liri kunyumba kwa [[Platanus|mitengo]] yakale ya [[Platanus|ndege]] . 

